snippet.title: C64 Game: Mystery Master - Felony!
snippet.description: Strategy detective game with an original set-up at the start in that you select a case to solve according to the hands on an analog clock. In-game you must make note of numbers in order to figure it out. http://www.lemon64.com/?mainurl=http%3A//www.lemon64.com/games/details.php%3FID%3D3676
